A video of two men trying to hijack a Range Rover has surfaced on
social media. The video was shared by anti-crime activist Yusuf Abramjee, and it
allegedly happened in Bryanston Johannesburg. In the video, the two men can be seen coming out of an Alfa Romeo
and running towards both sides of the Range Rover SUV. As they were about to reach the SUV, they start running back and the
driver get's out of the SUV, running towardsÂ them whiles shooting at them. It is not clear exactly when the incident took place. 